Class DataAbilityResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.aafwk.ability.DataAbilityResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Sequenceable

    public class DataAbilityResult
extends Object
implements Sequenceable
    Saves the data operation result.

    DataAbilityResult is used to save the result of a DataAbilityOperation performed on the database.
